What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Bicycle Tires Market?

Market Analysis and Size

Recently, there has been remarkable growth in bicycle tires market due to increasing awareness regarding the healthy lifestyle among major worldwide population. As a result, health enthusiasts are inclined toward performing physical activities such as cycling to stay healthy and fit from all across the globe. Therefore, there is remarkable growth in demand for bicycles globally, directly fuelling the need for the bicycle tires in the market. Apart from this, the continuously increasing fuel prices is one of the significant factors stimulating demand opportunities in the global market for bicycle tires.

